    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that presents very nicely and should make a fun, enjoyable driver for its next owner. It shows well overall, with the expected light signs of age and use, but it\u2019s clearly been cared for and has a lot to offer for someone who wants a solid, attractive example rather than a trailer queen. A great balance of usability, character, and value.",
