    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Priced at $5,400, this vehicle is in poor overall condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project, fixer-upper, or very basic budget transportation. It runs and drives, but it shows clear signs of age, wear, and neglect, and buyers should expect cosmetic flaws, a tired interior, and mechanical items that may need attention sooner rather than later. This is not a clean or fully sorted example, but for the right buyer who wants an inexpensive starting point, it could still be worthwhile. Please come prepared to inspect it carefully and expect to put money into it.",
      "price": 5400.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition example that shows well overall and should be a dependable, enjoyable driver for the next owner. The exterior presents nicely with the kind of light cosmetic wear and minor age-related blemishes you\u2019d expect on a used car, and the interior appears well kept with normal signs of use rather than excessive wear. This is not a perfect or fully restored show car, but it comes across as a solid, well-sorted vehicle that has been cared for and still has plenty to offer. A buyer should expect a nice driver with good overall presentation, typical used-car imperfections, and no attempt to hide that it\u2019s an older vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition example that offers a really nice mix of style, usability, and value. It presents well, has clearly been cared for, and should be an enjoyable car to own and drive. Not a mint showpiece, but a strong, honest car that\u2019s ready to be appreciated.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Practical, affordable, and priced to move, this vehicle is a solid opportunity for a buyer seeking straightforward transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used car, but it still offers real value as an inexpensive daily driver, backup vehicle, or project. If you're looking for low-cost entry into ownership, this is a compelling option at an accessible price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation or wants a straightforward project to tinker with. It\u2019s being offered honestly and priced fairly for what it is, with plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want a cheap car from a seller who\u2019s upfront and easy to deal with, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget daily with good bones and plenty of usable life left. The powertrain pulls cleanly, the drivetrain feels serviceable, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes upkeep affordable. Not a show car, but a capable runner with honest wear, strong utility, and real potential for someone who values function over cosmetics. A great entry point for an enthusiast, commuter backup, or practical fixer-upper.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
